list.abstract:
cabinet
n.
(有抽屉或格子的)橱柜, <美>内阁
adj.
<美>内阁的, 小巧的
cabinet
Cabinet has doors, and usually hanging on the wall or sitting on the floor, it uses for storage.
For example: We keep dishware, cups, bowls and plates in the kitchen cabinet.
橱柜
cabinet
n.（名词）
An upright, cupboardlike repository with shelves, drawers, or compartments for the safekeeping or display of a collection of objects or materials.
壁橱，橱柜：直立的，类似于柜橱的贮藏间，带有架子、抽屉或分隔间，用于保存或展示一批物品或物资
Often Cabinet A body of persons appointed by a head of state or a prime minister to head the executive departments of the government and to act as official advisers.
常作 Cabinet 内阁：受国家首脑或总理任命而领导政府执行部门并作为官方顾问的一个班底
Archaic A small or private room set aside for a specific activity.
【古语】 密室，小房间：为某专门活动而开设的一个小的或私人的房间
Rhode Island Southeastern Massachusetts See milk shake See Regional Note at milk shake
【罗德岛】 【麻省东南部】 参见 milk shake 参见 milk shake
adj.（形容词）
Suitable for storage or display in a cabinet, as because of size or decorative quality.
可展示的，可保存的：由于体积大小或包装质量的原因而适于在柜子中贮藏或展示的
Of, relating to, or being a member of a governmental cabinet:
内阁成员的：属于政府内阁一员的或与之相关的：
cabinet matters; a cabinet minister.
内阁成员的事务；内阁大臣
Used in the making of cabinets:
细木材的，柜材的：用于制造柜子的材料：
teak and other heavy cabinet wood.
柚木或其它用于制造柜子的重质木材
French
法语
partly from diminutive of Old North French cabine [gambling-room] perhaps alteration of Old French cabane [small house] * see cabin
部分为 古法国北方方言 cabine的小后缀 [赌博间] 可能为 古法语 cabane的变化 [小房子] *参见 cabin
and partly from Italian gabinetto [closet, chest of drawers] ; akin to Old North French cabine
并且部分源自 意大利语 gabinetto [壁橱，抽屉的空腔] ；类似于 古法国北方方言 cabine
[N., sense 4, possibly from the square wooden container in which the mixer was encased]
[名词的第四种意义，可能来源于包装混合物的方形木质容器]
cab“inetful
n.（名词）
cabinet
n.
橱柜
a medicine cabinet
药架
政府内阁
a Cabinet Minister
内阁部长
cabinet

yingyinNormal.en: What about perceived miscommunication between me and my Cabinet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 说是我跟内阁之间的意思传达有错误如何？

yingyinNormal.en: No, you're right. I don't believe in it. Two of my cabinet ministers are gay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说得对，我是不信。我两个内阁成员还是同性恋呢。

yingyinNormal.en: As I accept all of your letters of resignation and dissolve my old cabinet, I wanna welcome each and every one of you to my new cabinet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我正式接受各位的辞呈并解散我的旧内阁，然后我想欢迎在座的各位加入我的新内阁。

yingyinNormal.en: Douglas, will you give us a minute? Of course. I'll be with the cabinet, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 道格拉斯，能让我们单独谈谈吗？当然。我会跟内阁在一起，先生。

yingyinNormal.en: Did he promise a cabinet position? More than that? He offered to put you on the ticket, didn't he?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他保证给你内阁席位？还不止吗？他要带你一起竞选，是吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You will hand over your delegates, and you will serve on in my cabinet. And we will forget that any of this ever happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要交出你的代表继续在我的内阁任职，我们忘掉发生过的这一切。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not gonna start selling off cabinet positions before I've won the White House. Those decisions will be based purely on merit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在入主白宫之前我不会出卖内阁席位。这种决定应该完全按资质做出。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I thought it'd tickle you. Have you got a lab report? Yeah, Charlie Welsborough's the son of a Cabinet Minister, so I'm under a lot of pressure to get a result.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我就猜你会笑。法医报告带来了吗？带了，查理·韦尔斯伯鲁是内阁大臣的儿子，所以这个案子我压力很大。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, guys, guys, did you see my new, china cabinet? Uh-huh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂，你们看到我的新瓷器柜了吗？哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Why don't we just find a place for it? Okay. How about in that cabinet?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们为什么不找个地方放它？放在那个柜子里？

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, hey, have you ever locked yourself in a TV cabinet, VD boy? Monkey lover.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你曾经把自己锁在电视柜里吗？性病小子。猴子爱人。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything changes, Jim. Everything evolves. Some things are perfect just the way they are. Asteroids. People don't live inside an Asteroids arcade cabinet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么都在变，吉姆。都在发展。有些本身就很完美。比如"爆破彗星"。现实是人们并不活在街机里面。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone is looking for Mr. Skinny Legs. Mr. Skinny Legs is not in the filing cabinet. Oh. Mr. Skinny Legs is not under the chair. Ooh. Mr. Skinny Legs is not on the table. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都在找瘦腿先生。瘦腿先生并没有在文件柜里。哦！瘦腿先生也没有在椅子下面。哦！瘦腿先生也没有在桌子上面。哦！
